{{Green politics sidebar |expanded=all}}

{{Politics of Vanuatu}}
The '''Greens/Verts''' is a [[green politics|green]] [[political party]] in [[Vanuatu]].
At [[Vanuatuan general election, 2008|the last legislative elections]], 2 September 2008, the party won 2 out of 52 seats. Its most prominent member is [[Moana Carcasses Kalosil]], the deputy leader of the opposition and a former cabinet minister.

